----
Definition:
1\Empty or
2\A node with a key and a list of child trees

Eg:
 1\Empty:
             
 2\Tree with one node
                                        Les
 3\Tree with two nodes:               
 
                                         Les
                                        /    \
                                     Cathy  Sally
                                     
---
Terminology:
  Root: Top node in the tree
  Ancestor: parent or parent of parent
  Descendants: child or child of child
  Sibiling: have the same parents
  Leaf: node with no children
  level:1+num edges between root and node
  Height: Maximum depth of subtree node and farthest leaf
  
  
  
  
